import React from 'react'
import {StyleSheet} from 'react-native'

const CreateAccountStyles = StyleSheet.create({
    container: {
        flexDirection:'column',
        flex:1,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems:'center',
        /* backgroundColor: '#ddd', */
        borderRadius: '5',
        width: 500,
        height:400,
      
    input:{
        margin: 15,
        height: 40,
        width: 300,
        borderColor: '#7a42f4',
        borderWidth: 1,
        marginBottom: 20,
        shadowColor: '#000',
        shadowOffset: {
          width: 0,
          height: 2,
        },
        shadowOpacity: 0.23,
        shadowRadius: 2.62,
        elevation: 4,
        },
    }
})

export default CreateAccountStyles
